{"tid":1878183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安倍晉三冀增加口罩產量至每月逾六億隻","createTime":"2020-02-13T12:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T12:31:17.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62d5e68681bd20c70019ca96ecffabef870e42c9","tid":1878183,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"日本和歌山縣一名50歲男醫生確診感染新型冠狀病毒. 這名醫生上月31號起發燒和全身感到倦怠, 本月3至5號曾服用退燒藥, 期間繼續在他就職位於湯淺町的醫院上班, 今天確診染病. 病人發病前, 並沒有前往中國, 是和歌山縣首宗個案.<br />\n<br />\n        東京確診個案增至4宗. 新增個案病人是的士司機, 他報稱曾經接載相信是中國人的乘客, 當局正調查他的感染途徑.<br />\n<br />\n        停泊在橫濱檢疫旳鑽石公主號郵輪, 再多44人包括一名船員確診染病, 令船上感染人數上升至218人. 連同其他個案, 日本至今有至少249宗確診個案.<br />\n<br />\n        首相安倍晉三, 回應口罩持續短缺的問題時表示, 會致力增加供應, 希望每月產量達到上月供應量兩倍的超過6億隻. 另外, 有報道指, 防衛省已基本決定, 召集應急預備自衛官和預備自衛官, 以應對擴大的疫情.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20200213192657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200213192657&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5Ivc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=1827a57d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20200213192657</a>"},{"pid":"c354660e2acb1c1319aeb7eb8bd7a5c81a8c6e56","tid":1878183,"uid":15564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg11-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/84598021_2486098501708020_3508579833737117696_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=743PeMXJBXAAX9KsVGl&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg11-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=14&amp;oh=79f182665edad18b663cbeb2d2a0dbbc&amp;oe=5ED19C81\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg11-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F84598021_2486098501708020_3508579833737117696_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3D743PeMXJBXAAX9KsVGl%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg11-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D14%26oh%3D79f182665edad18b663cbeb2d2a0dbbc%26oe%3D5ED19C81&h=50c49bd0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}